00:20:01,040 --> 00:20:01,600
Give us back Qingdao!

342
00:20:01,760 --> 00:20:02,720
Down with traitors!

343
00:20:02,800 --> 00:20:03,760
We want justice!

344
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:05,360
We want justice!

345
00:20:07,280 --> 00:20:07,680
Come on.

346
00:20:07,920 --> 00:20:09,920
Let's close all the windows.

347
00:20:10,240 --> 00:20:11,120
Even if you build a wall,

348
00:20:11,360 --> 00:20:12,560
