528
00:28:47,840 --> 00:28:49,920
and try to win their sympathy and support.

529
00:28:50,560 --> 00:28:54,400
If this scheme can't be accepted,

530
00:28:56,240 --> 00:28:57,520
then I'm afraid,

531
00:29:01,280 --> 00:29:02,080
we can only wait for death.

532
00:29:07,760 --> 00:29:11,520
Shandong Province is the cradle of Chinese civilization.

533
00:29:08,471 --> 00:29:14,031
[U.S. Delegation Residence, Paris]

534
00:29:13,600 --> 00:29:16,080
It is the birthplace of Confucius and Mencius.

535
00:29:17,280 --> 00:29:19,760
It is a holy place for the Chinese people.

536
00:29:20,080 --> 00:29:23,040
We wish you can protect China's interests

537
00:29:23,280 --> 00:29:25,040
by diplomatic means.

538
00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:26,960
Please help us.

539
00:29:31,920 --> 00:29:32,800
Good to see you, sir.

540
00:29:33,520 --> 00:29:34,080
Good to see you.

541
00:29:34,160 --> 00:29:34,720
Me too.

542
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:35,760
Good to see you.

543
00:29:35,840 --> 00:29:36,400
Me too.

544
00:29:37,680 --> 00:29:38,480
Cabinet Minister Lu,

545
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:41,280
I've conveyed your messages three times

546
00:29:41,360 --> 00:29:43,520
to President Wilson.

547
00:29:43,840 --> 00:29:46,000
He is not available to meet with you tonight.

548
00:29:46,560 --> 00:29:48,240
He asked that you leave the files

549
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:49,920
