551
00:29:58,320 --> 00:29:59,600
If there is any doubt,

552
00:29:59,840 --> 00:30:01,360
you can call me anytime.

553
00:30:02,080 --> 00:30:03,360
Please tell him,

554
00:30:03,680 --> 00:30:04,480
that tonight

555
00:30:04,720 --> 00:30:07,040
